---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="CI/CD Transformation"
  descripcion="Replace fragile, manual deployments with automated, auditable CI/CD pipelines. GitHub Actions, ArgoCD, and trunk-based development that ships to production in minutes."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #0d2f50 100%); padding: 100px 24px 80px;"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #60A5FA; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        Solution · CI/CD Transformation
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        From deploy anxiety to<br />deploy confidence.
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10"
        style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.9);"
      >
        Automated CI/CD pipelines that test, build, scan, and deploy with zero
        manual steps. Ship to production multiple times per day without
        coordination overhead.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
          style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);"
        >
          Transform your pipelines
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all hover:bg-white/10"
          style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);"
        >
          View case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key points -->
  <section style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">
          End-to-end pipeline automation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">
          From the first commit to production deployment — automated, audited,
          and reversible at every stage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {
          [
            {
              title: 'GitHub Actions pipeline design',
              desc: 'Composable workflows for build, test, security scanning (Trivy, SAST), Docker image build & ECR push, and environment-specific deployments. Reusable across repositories.',
              icon: 'M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z',
            },
            {
              title: 'Progressive delivery & rollbacks',
              desc: 'Canary and blue/green deployments with automatic rollback on failed health checks. Deploy with confidence — reverting a bad release takes one git command.',
              icon: 'M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99',
            },
            {
              title: 'Security integrated into every pipeline',
              desc: 'Container image scanning, dependency vulnerability checks, SAST analysis, and secrets detection — all automated before code reaches staging. Security left, not bolted on.',
              icon: 'M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z',
            },
            {
              title: 'Trunk-based development enablement',
              desc: 'Feature flags, short-lived branches, and automated environment provisioning per PR. Eliminate long-lived feature branches and the merge conflicts that come with them.',
              icon: 'M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5',
            },
          ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7"
              style="border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                style="background: #EEF4FF;"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  style="color: #1E6FFF;"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    d={icon}
                  />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #0A2540;">
                {title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
                {desc}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Ready to ship with confidence?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">
        Let's audit your current deployment process and design a pipeline that
        removes the bottlenecks.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
        style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,111,255,0.45);"
      >
        Audit my pipelines
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          ><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- See it in practice -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8" style="border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="section-label">See it in practice</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-3" style="color: #0A2540;">Three CI/CD implementations</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-5">
          <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">aws-terraform-devops</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: #F0FDF4; color: #15803D; border: 1px solid #BBF7D0;">Production</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">Dual pipelines — GitHub Actions (OIDC) + Jenkins (on-premise). SonarCloud 80% coverage gate blocks every merge. ECR push → EKS deploy.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/projects/aws-terraform-devops" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Case study →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/aws-terraform-devops" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">gitops-stack</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: #F0FDF4; color: #15803D; border: 1px solid #BBF7D0;">Production</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">Jenkins CI: Build → Test → Deploy to EKS. Ansible config management. SSM for access — zero SSH keys. git push to production in under 8 minutes.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/projects/gitops-stack" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Case study →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/gitops-stack" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">linux-fleet-manager</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: #F0FDF4; color: #15803D; border: 1px solid #BBF7D0;">Production</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">Bash + SSH fleet management — no agents. ShellCheck validation in CI. Idempotent scripts safe for re-runs. Red Hat engineering standards.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/projects/linux-fleet-manager" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Case study →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/linux-fleet-manager" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
